[2026-03-09T00:46:16Z] [llm] {"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-6","id":"msg_01ENk76aEbMNBfNg4VEuzCSQ","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"tool_use","id":"toolu_016rxXWKLdAGvAFe6m4ePPxV","name":"Edit","input":{"replace_all":false,"file_path":"/workspace/docs/USAGE.md","old_string":"cloche init [--workflow <name>] [--image <base>]\n```\n\n| Flag | Default | Description |\n|------|---------|-------------|\n| `--workflow <name>` | `develop` | Workflow name. Creates `.cloche/<name>.cloche`. |\n| `--image <base>` | `ubuntu:24.04` | Base Docker image for the generated Dockerfile. |\n\nCreates `.cloche/` with a workflow file, Dockerfile, configuration file\n(`config.toml`), and prompt templates (`implement.md`, `fix.md`,\n`update-docs.md`). Skips files that already exist.\nAlso adds gitignore entries for runtime state directories.","new_string":"cloche init [--workflow <name>] [--base-image <image>]\n```\n\n| Flag | Default | Description |\n|------|---------|-------------|\n| `--workflow <name>` | `develop` | Workflow name. Creates `.cloche/<name>.cloche`. |\n| `--base-image <image>` | `cloche-base:latest` | Base Docker image for the generated Dockerfile. |\n\nCreates `.cloche/` with a workflow file, Dockerfile, configuration file\n(`config.toml`), prompt templates (`implement.md`, `fix.md`,\n`update-docs.md`), a host orchestration workflow (`host.cloche`), a\nprompt generation script (`scripts/prepare-prompt.sh`), and a version\nfile. Skips files that already exist.\nAlso adds gitignore entries for runtime state directories."},"caller":{"type":"direct"}}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":1,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1154,"cache_read_input_tokens":77265,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1154},"output_tokens":8,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"5ad63e92-d8fd-45c5-affb-b4